<div class="goldline">K I N G S .</div></h2></div><div class="col3"><b>Turfside</b> is a sim game centered around the sport of Thoroughbred flat racing, here to revolutionize the RPG experience on dA and allow anyone to play <b>without the need for art, literature, or money.</b> Train and race your equine athletes with a click of the button, breed for success, and rise to the top of the leader board.

Using realistic horse genetics and detailed game mechanics, <b>Turfside</b> is an interactive experience everyone is welcome to participate in. Think you have what it takes to produce champions?
